               . That word upon which the whole Streſs of the Argument depends, is Matheteuſate, which ſignifies, to make Diſciples. The Learned render Mathetes, a Scholar, a Diſciple; and Matheteuo, to be a Scholar, or Diſciple. And upon this word in this place, the Greek Lexicon renders it, to make Diſciples.
